OL,6,FThere are also about 6,500 people
OL,7,Fwaiting for an allotment.
OL,9,Frent increases are still going ahead.
OL,11,FAccording to cabinet reports, new
OL,12,Fdiscounts will be offered including
OL,13,Ffor people on low incomes, or with
OL,14,Fplots that flood or are overgrown.
OL,16,FJon James, head of natural and marine
OL,17,Fenvironment, said: "We've had
OL,18,Fmaintenance and staffing budgets
OL,19,Freduced. That's resulted in a decline
OL,20,Fin what we can actually do.
