OL,6,F"We've looked at what investment we
OL,7,Fneed to make so that we can start
OL,8,Fimproving and addressing the backlog
OL,9,Fof maintenance, like repairs to water
OL,10,Fsupply and fences.
OL,12,F"We're currently just responding to
OL,13,Feffectively emergency work. We're not
OL,14,Fin a position where we can proactively
OL,15,Fmanage our sites. That's what we want
OL,16,Fto focus the income on, so we can
OL,17,Fstart a programme of work addressing
OL,18,Fthat."
