OL,4,Cas council plans to double rent
OL,6,FCouncil officers estimated how much
OL,7,Fthey need to spend to address the
OL,8,Fmaintenance backlog over the next 15
OL,9,Fyears, and used that figure to come to
OL,10,Fthe proposed rent increases.
OL,12,FThe target is to raise #55,000 extra
OL,13,Fincome from rents, to help pay the
OL,14,Fongoing maintenance.
OL,16,FPatsy Mellor, director of management
OL,17,Fof place, added: "We heavily subsidise
OL,18,Fthe allotment service, but we've
OL,19,Freduced that subsidy by about #55,000
OL,20,Fby increasing the rent.
